{"tid":1586733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"驚獅鳥失去國際支持嘅人，新疆咁多單恐襲案，失去左支持未","createTime":"2019-09-22T06:05:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T16:25:44.000Z","uid":21699,"like":41,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"4e9815db3433853592b5c53409cb20e57215a8b1","tid":1586733,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T06:05:46.000Z","msg":"人地喺地鐵斬人，然後被中共文宣瘋狂抺黑。基本上你喺bbc/cnn comment session提起新疆集中營，班中國人就會用新疆恐襲黎反駁你。但點解恐襲左咁多單，都未失去過國際支持？<br />\n<br />\n西方國家官員有自己情報網，好明顯對方知道民族清洗係因，恐襲反抗先係果，。西方傳媒都明白事情嘅root cause係邊，唔會因為民眾暴力反抗而淨係focus報導事情表面經過。<br />\n<br />\n獅鳥會唔會令到我地失去國際支持？我話唔會。因為大家都係出師有名。我地應該係文宣宣傳點解要獅鳥，而唔係停止獅鳥<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TUtXsmX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTUtXsmX.png&h=d1814ad3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E6%81%90%E6%80%96%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2596%2586%25E6%2581%2590%25E6%2580%2596%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E5%258B%2595%25E5%2588%2597%25E8%25A1%25A8&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FTYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=bf455866\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E6%81%90%E6%80%96%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8</a>"},{"pid":"acc4dec630c9d877c15f9eca1416574a27019459","tid":1586733,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T06:06:52.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"a6fb9be656b4c8c8b490bf2b5621406800eac5b8","tid":1586733,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T06:08:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ffe50061be807d4e152324f075c8f289553b4167","tid":1586733,"uid":287369,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T06:09:25.000Z","msg":"不是獅鳥，是自衛"},{"pid":"3436477ab439fdced75366d3e674fa5b4b8ffc89","tid":1586733,"uid":63406,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"